</div></div> <div id="cs_control_5579016" class="cs_control CS_Element_Custom"><style>blockquote {border-left: 5px solid #fff;}</style>
<div class="Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix">
<h2>Other Resources</h2>
<p>More information about water quality within the Mississippi National River and Recreation Area (Minnesota) may be found in the<em> </em><a href="http://stateoftheriver.com/" id="http://stateoftheriver.com/|"><em>State of the River</em> report</a>.<br />
<br />
The <em>River of History</em> discusses the history represented within the 72 mile corridor of the Mississippi National River and Recreation Area, including the history of Native Americans and dispossession, exploration, transportation, commerce, navigation, and other topics. <a href="https://www.nps.gov/miss/learn/historyculture/historic_resources.htm" id="https://www.nps.gov/miss/learn/historyculture/historic_resources.htm|">The <em>River of History</em> is provided online</a>.</p>
</div></div>
</td></tr>
</table></div>
